abstract_ssm: The collection is primarily composed of newspapers published in Brooklyn, New York, dating from the 18th century to 2016. It also includes a selection of newspapers published in Queens, Long Island, upstate New York, and New Jersey. In addition to paper editions, the collection includes microfilm copies of certain publications.
